<BLOCKQUOTE>
<HR>
Heimdall-RN wrote:<BR>
<DIV>You can channel your spells, and a lot more often than you're leading us to beleive- and at casting times less than 3 in all cases (though paladin heals are close enough after Focus I'll grant).&nbsp; At this point I'd rather see knights get -1DI, and warriors get -3 DI.</DIV><BR>
