		" 
			>
			<div></div><p>If your looking at Downward scaling tools, Tanking is kinda redundant to have scaling downwards. There really is no point in increasing your durability against weaker mobs, really it's moot point. So I think you might find more benifit from looking at other areas that can be scaled vs content in that way.</p><p>Like for instance, Melee Damage. If your melee damage increased against lower level mobs in relation to the tank, this would provide extra power against lower level mobs. Other things could be an increase in other melee effects, like Reposte, Stun etc the point being that as you need to be less of a powerhouse tank you can lay down the offensive instead.</p>	
